reviewText: 3yr old daughter was starting to read before the DVD, but upon watching it a few times, she lept forward. She is talking to us more about how words sound and what they sound like in the beginning/end of words.  It gets children more in the mode of reading and stimulates them to learn.Well worth the price in my opinion.  Just wish there are more of these to buy.
